  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p> </p><p>These are exciting times for holders of insurance stocks, whether institutional investors or insurance executives themselves. Approximately 70% of the world’s insurance premiums are written by stockholder-owned insurers, so rising share prices provides added financial security to all stakeholders in the insurance value chain.</p><p><a href=\"https://internationalinsurance.org/sites/default/files/2019-08/GISR_Q2_2019.pdf\"><strong>read more &gt;</strong></a></p></div></body></html>",
